a.n: Tonya Baker: Live at Jazz a Vienne Festival

p.k: Psalmist, gifted songwriter, author, instructor, workshop instructor, and gospel singer Tonya Baker travels the world to share her gift of singing and her great wisdom.
p.d: Psalmist, gifted songwriter, author, instructor, workshop instructor, and gospel singer Tonya Baker travels the world to share her gift of singing and her great wisdom. Over the past decade, Baker has collaborated on the albums of several renowned gospel artists. She is a distinguished guest at several renowned festivals, such as the Jazz Festival in Vienna.
